OL,3,C'Adored' woman died after falling into
OL,4,Cpub cellar
OL,6,FThe owners of a pub where a woman died
OL,7,Fafter falling into the cellar while
OL,8,Fdecorating for her daughter's birthday
OL,9,Fhave been spared prison.
OL,11,FOlwen Collier had gone to the Stag and
OL,12,FPheasant pub in Carmel in January 2023
OL,13,Fto prepare for her daughter's birthday
OL,14,Fcelebrations.
OL,16,FShe suffered serious head injuries
OL,17,Fafter falling down into the cellar of
OL,18,Fthe Carmarthenshire pub in what Judge
OL,19,FPaul Thomas KC called a "fatal
OL,20,Faccident waiting to happen."
