OL,6,FJudge Thomas said that dim lighting,
OL,7,Fpoor signage and unclear directions
OL,8,Fled Mrs Collier to enter the unlocked
OL,9,Fcellar, where she fell down the stairs
OL,10,Fand later died.
OL,12,FTracy and Philip Hawkins, the owners
OL,13,Fof the pub, appeared at Swansea Crown
OL,14,FCourt on Monday, 22 April.
OL,16,FThe pair, both of Llandeilo Road, had
OL,17,Fpreviously pleaded guilty to failing
OL,18,Fto discharge general health and safety
OL,19,Fduty to a person other than an
OL,20,Femployee.
