OL,3,C'Adored' woman died after falling into
OL,4,Cpub cellar
OL,6,FThe court heard that Mrs Collier had
OL,7,Farrived at the pub and was directed to
OL,8,Fthe function room by Philip Hawkins,
OL,9,F49, who was working alone while his
OL,10,Fwife, 53, was ill in bed.
OL,12,FMr Hawkins had been taking gas
OL,13,Fcanisters down into the cellar and had
OL,14,Fleft the door unlocked. The light was
OL,15,Foff and could only be turned from
OL,16,Fbehind the bar.
