OL,3,C'Adored' woman died after falling into
OL,4,Cpub cellar
OL,6,FThe prosecution said that Mrs
OL,7,FCollier's grandson, who was with her
OL,8,Fat the time, had tried to grab her as
OL,9,Fshe slipped down the stairs but had
OL,10,Fbeen unable to keep hold.
OL,12,FThe defence said the couple were
OL,13,F"broken people" following the incident.
OL,15,FThey were both handed 18 weeks in
OL,16,Fprison, suspended for 12 months. Mr
OL,17,FHawkins, who was considered more
OL,18,Fculpable by the judge, was also
OL,19,Fordered to complete 150 hours of
OL,20,Funpaid work.
