OL,6,FJudge Thomas said: "The word tragic is
OL,7,Foften overused, even in these courts.
OL,8,FThis case, however, fully merits that
OL,9,Fdescription.
OL,11,F"What was meant to be a joyous family
OL,12,Foccasion turned into the saddest of
OL,13,Fevents. A healthy and adored lady lost
OL,14,Fher life, leaving her family utterly
OL,15,Fbereft and inconsolable and that
OL,16,Fhappened because you two did not take
OL,17,Fsufficient, even the most basic, care
OL,18,Ffor the safety of your customers."
