OL,6,FHe added that, while he was sure the
OL,7,Ffamily would want him to "throw away
OL,8,Fthe key" and described what happened
OL,9,Fas a "thoughtless error with
OL,10,Fdevastating consequences," he did not
OL,11,Ffeel an immediate custodial sentence
OL,12,Fwas appropriate.
